{{Expand German|Kulturattaché|date=October 2014}}

A '''cultural [[attaché]]''' is a [[diplomacy|diplomat]] with the responsibility of promoting the [[culture]] of his or her homeland. Historically, the post has often been filled by [[writer]]s and [[artist]]s, giving them a steady [[income]], and allowing them to develop their own creative work, while promoting their own country's culture abroad.

